                                                                                                 A.2.2.2 Subscriber Client Node and Token
                                                                                                 Subscribers (e.g., Subscriber 1 in the figure)with a key generation capability may request key
                                                                                                 translation from a KTC (e.g., using path A) to be sent to other subscribers. These keys may be
                                                                                                 stored by the client node or on the subscriber's token (if used).
